comments: RAR shows Winslow (MIA) is already in Poythress' (ATL) path and the two briefly engage after the legal screen.
[Observable in enhanced video] McGruder (MIA) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
RAR shows Poythress (ATL) jumps from point A to point B into McGruder (MIA) and affects his shot attempt.
RAR shows Adebayo (MIA) makes clean hand-on-ball contact during Poythress' (ATL) shot attempt.
PXP and RAR show Poythress' (ATL) hand never reaches Adebayo's (MIA) opposite hip and there is no pause in the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Adebayo (MIA) moves his pivot foot heel to toe to create distance.
LAR shows Huerter (ATL) makes contact to McGruder's (MIA) arm that affects his ability to secure the pass.
Adebayo (MIA) is already in Huerter's (ATL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Possession is correctly awarded to ATL.
Winslow (MIA) makes marginal contact with Young (ATL) that does not affect his shot near the rim.
Bembry (ATL) makes marginal body contact with Wade (MIA), but he is able to move through it and finish his driving shot attempt.
McGruder (MIA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Young's (ATL) drive.
Young (ATL) leaves his feet to pass and he returns to the floor while still in possession of the ball.
Carter (ATL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Poythress (ATL) makes incidental contact with Wade (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Wade (MIA) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two legal steps after his gather.
Wade (MIA) extends his leg as part of his natural shooting motion, any contact with Poythress (ATL) is considered incidental.
Poythress (ATL) legally contests Wade's (MIA) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
RAR shows Carter (ATL) makes marginal contact with Olynyk (MIA) as he defends the shot near the rim.
RLS shows Bembry (ATL) makes marginal contact with Olynyk (MIA) that does not affect his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Carter (ATL) makes marginal contact with Olynyk (MIA) prior to cleanly dislodging the ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (Hawks ball) was confirmed.
McGruder (MIA) jumps into Bazemore's (ATL) lower body and affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Bazemore (ATL) attempts to commit a take foul on Richardson (MIA), but contact is marginal.
